    ALLOW CUSTOMERS TO CREATE THEIR

    OWN DESIGN

    Customily's online product designer software gives customers the power to personalize any design on your Shopify eCommerce site. The ability to upload custom designs, and let customers personalize them by adding custom text and images guarantees an amazing looking product, increasing the value of of your product catalog and also increasing customers engagement and loyalty.

    ​

    Our online preview tool seamlessly integrates with Shopify, giving customers the ability to see what they'll get while they design. Our web to print tools then provide you with high resolution files of your customers design ready for production, where it be printing, engraving or embroidery. 

    ​

    With our custom product designer selling personalized products on Shopify has never been so easy!

    HOW DOES IT WORK?

    Integrate Customily app to your Shopify store and let your customers order personalized products right from your site. Process orders faster, better, error-free with print ready output files. Start selling customized products like cell cases, mugs, tshirts, jewelry, bags, business cards, flyers and SO MUCH MORE...

    INTEGRATION COMPLETE

    CUSTOMILY'S ADMIN

    Customily's Admin allows you to transform your static products into customizable ones. Manage products, set personalization areas and parameters, define output methods for printing and engraving, upload artworks, fonts, colors, pictures, masks and other settings.

    SHOPIFY'S ADMIN

    Once Customily is installed, our software pulls the products along with their details from your Shopify store, and links them with Customily's Admin .

    You can define which products from your store can or cannot be customized, add your different personalization options (such as text input, picture upload, color selection, etc.) directly from your Shopify Admin panel.

    ONLINE PRODUCT

    DESIGNER

    Once you save all the settings, the dynamic personalization will automatically appear on your product page.

    Instead of a static and boring product picture, customers will see a real dynamic preview of your product, which they will use to design within the specified personalization parameters.

    Customily's online product designer is fully responsive, producing high quality previews for web and mobile.

    ​

    ​

    CUSTOMERS ORDER PLACED

    WEB TO PRINT

    Your orders will appear as usual on your Shopify Admin panel, only this time there will also be a link to download the ready to print file. 

    No more need to manually process orders, since Customily will provide you your client's designs ready for production in files like EPS, Ai, PDF, PNG, DXF for printing or engraving.
